      "writtenOn": "2026-05-14T16:27:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Its very simple in the end - no guides needed IMO.\n\nHello world examples, bump, etc are very simple - they are not an \"artwork\". Despite you write by hand or AI. Of course when added in a new file in our project in new file, it has copyright header - but nothing happens is someone has stolen it.\n\nAnything more complex is human added \"artwork\" - hand written or generated without ANY manual edit.\n\nAdding coauthored in only subject of taste to show to world - I am as quickly as I am because of AI.\n\nAFAICT that\u0027s the real work explanation - contact legal if you want 😄",
      "revId": "86f2b1c2ab6fc0122cf117acd323f065fa759676",
      "serverId": "6d2eb258-4fe2-443e-8a38-ca81da23d4c2"
